# ScribLink Development Quick Reference

## 🏗️ Project Structure
See [project-structure.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/project-structure.mdc) for complete architecture overview.

## 🎨 Styling & Theming
- **CSS Variables**: Always use variables from [style.css](mdc:src/style.css)
- **Color Palette**: Neutral colors only - no bright reds/blues/teals
- **Layout**: Use `100vw`/`100vh` for full viewport coverage
- **Details**: [css-guidelines.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/css-guidelines.mdc)

## ⚡ Vue.js Patterns
- **Composition API**: Always use Composition API with `<script setup>`
- **Event Handling**: Props down, events up with data
- **Reactive State**: Use `ref()` and `computed()`
- **Details**: [vue-patterns.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/vue-patterns.mdc)

## 🔧 JavaScript & API
- **Service Layer**: Use [apiServices.js](mdc:src/services/apiServices.js) for all API calls
- **Error Handling**: Always use try-catch with descriptive logging
- **Note Creation**: Use consistent pattern with response.note ID
- **Details**: [javascript-patterns.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/javascript-patterns.mdc)

## 📝 Markdown Editor
- **NoteEditor**: [NoteEditor.vue](mdc:src/components/NoteEditor.vue) - Full-screen layout
- **SummaryPanel**: [SummaryPanel.vue](mdc:src/components/SummaryPanel.vue) - Scrollable content box
- **Click-to-Edit**: Preview mode with click-to-edit functionality
- **Details**: [markdown-editor.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/markdown-editor.mdc)

## 🐛 Common Issues & Solutions
- **"Note with ID new not found"**: Use response.note ID for selection
- **Layout Issues**: Use 100vw/100vh for full coverage
- **Color Inconsistencies**: Always use CSS variables
- **Details**: [common-patterns.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/common-patterns.mdc)

## 🔍 Debugging
- **Console Logging**: Use emoji prefixes (🔍, ✅, ❌, ⚠️)
- **API Responses**: Always log responses for debugging
- **State Changes**: Log component state updates
- **Details**: [debugging-guide.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/debugging-guide.mdc)

